restaurant.description:
Two Michelin starred The Tasting Room is the perfect place in Macau to experience contemporary French cuisine. Originating from the French Alps, Executive Chef Fabrice Vulin carefully selects the season’s most delicious ingredients from around the world using his intricate and very intimate relationships with his suppliers which, allows him to create meticulously and artistically presented dishes that trigger all your senses.

The front of house team, guided by Restaurant Manager Julien Gardin, welcomes you with the utmost genuineness and provides a relaxed yet professional service that will take you on a journey through Fabrice’s creations with warmth and elegance.

The Tasting Room also has a Private Dining room that can welcome up to 14 guests for more private occasions.

restaurant.description:
Voyages by Alain Ducasse explores classic French flavors and showcases bistro favorites with a contemporary and generous approach. Using upmarket ingredients and expert techniques, Executive Chef Anthony Bacle takes Voyages to new culinary pinnacles, revisiting classics such as Parisian-style beef tartare, cheese soufflé, onion soup, roasted French chicken and Koulibiak salmon.

The decadent dessert menu includes delicious temptations such as Grand Marnier Soufflé, velvety Crème Caramel, and a delightfully refreshing Passion Fruit and Coconut Vacherin.

Tantalizing the taste buds even further is the Bar at Voyages, where Head Bartender Norbert Szasz welcomes guests with custom-made concoctions with a distinct twist.

With its stylish cocktail bar and fresh take on classic French cuisine, guests can indulge in familiar dishes, while creating fond memories in a uniquely vibrant and modern setting.
restaurant.name: Voyages by Alain Ducasse

The exclusive 38 Lounge on the top floor of Altira Macau offers an ultra-stylish experience like no other. While the outdoor terrace opens up to unrivalled views of the Macau peninsula, the main hall indoors is the spot for incredible music performances.

38 Lounge is the perfect place for those special gatherings such as Birthdays, 100 Day Celebrations, Weddings and Anniversaries. Our dedicated staff will make your event truly memorable.
